{"tid":1288493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【宣傳】夢遊後需要出國散心支援","createTime":"2019-07-05T16:01:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T14:42:15.000Z","uid":258197,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a3360cd0bd524ce9090b635121fa4f0f510c82ae","tid":1288493,"uid":258197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:01:51.000Z","msg":"反送中受傷被捕者人道支援基金心理支援熱線︰<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">98456641</span><br />\n如果有手足夢遊完好需要出國遊行既話<br />\n可以打依個電話　<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">98456641</span></strong><br />\n入面會有人接聽你電話後轉介去律師樓傾下你個Case 大唔大風險<br />\n如果大風險會直接搵依個基金既臨時信託人（吳靄儀、何韻詩、許寶強及何秀蘭）<br />\n再根據你既情況支援你既需要<br />\n<br />\nFacebook 主頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/612Fund/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F612Fund%2F&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=1a4cb227\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/612Fund/</a><br />\n其中一個Post︰<br />\n// 各位朋友，<br />\n本基金為所有因反送中運動而受傷、被捕的人，提供醫療、法律、心理等人道支援。<br />\n如你⭕沒有受傷、亦⭕沒有被捕，但是，現在⭕很擔心自己可能被捕，想了解多一點相關風險／可能面對的處境，請你亦可以聯絡我們。基金會轉介法律諮詢服務，相關費用由基金支付。<br />\n請主動聯絡我們，你的資料，我們會保密。<br />\n各位保重。<br />\n<br />\n秘書處<br />\n反送中傷者被捕者人道支援基金<br />\n<br />\ntg : @ReliefFund612 <br />\npage inbox<br />\nwhatsapp / call +852 9845 6641//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/616%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%93%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E7%B1%8C%E6%AC%BE%E9%87%91%E9%A1%8D%E9%80%BE700%E8%90%AC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F616%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258F%25B4%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%2591-%25E7%25B1%258C%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E9%2587%2591%25E9%25A1%258D%25E9%2580%25BE700%25E8%2590%25AC%2F&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=e50deb8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F616%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258F%25B4%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%2591-%25E7%25B1%258C%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E9%2587%2591%25E9%25A1%258D%25E9%2580%25BE700%25E8%2590%25AC%2F&h=0cfaf145\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/616%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%93%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E7%B1%8C%E6%AC%BE%E9%87%91%E9%A1%8D%E9%80%BE700%E8%90%AC/</a><br />\n<br />\n有手足開過既post都有提過依個電話︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1284925/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1284925/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n如果可以既話Share出去比更多人睇<br />\n好多手足夢遊完好驚好唔知點算，想搵人幫手但又唔知搵邊個／點同人講既話<br />\n依度可能可以幫到你"},{"pid":"ae3de11e9545dd21558e8eb97631dd8dd5e4fc7a","tid":1288493,"uid":258197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2033ca96cf007b7087771309578f91b725eb2f2d","tid":1288493,"uid":258197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:15:09.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b3f74eeb5c2f3c096b29e41df5b2b876884cef","tid":1288493,"uid":14125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:16:15.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n<code>我無嘢講 我要見律師 我要驗傷 我唔解鎖電話 我唔簽任何文件</code>"},{"pid":"0a2dc5eb3e61dd065fd6f92927cb117ebd1beea0","tid":1288493,"uid":65790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:16:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f32e19fb6b66a54dc526eccaf2fa75e061a1478","tid":1288493,"uid":258197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:21:40.000Z","msg":"推到更多人見到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac5e2d553244ba4fbb288c480be3e22eca0edb0","tid":1288493,"uid":2